  "sn18.8:4.9": "“Aniccā, bhante” …",
  "sn18.8:4.10": "“evaṃ passaṃ, rāhula, sutavā ariyasāvako rūpataṇhāyapi nibbindati … pe …",
  "sn18.8:4.11": "saddataṇhāyapi nibbindati …",
  "sn18.8:4.12": "gandhataṇhāyapi nibbindati …",
  "sn18.8:4.13": "rasataṇhāyapi nibbindati …",
  "sn18.8:4.14": "phoṭṭhabbataṇhāyapi nibbindati …",
  "sn18.8:4.15": "dhammataṇhāyapi nibbindati … pe …",
  "sn18.8:4.16": "pajānātī”ti.",
